# Utilities and Helper Functions

## Core Utilities
- [bem/area_constraints.py](mdc:bem/area_constraints.py): Functions for mesh area constraints
- [bem/evaluate.py](mdc:bem/evaluate.py): Evaluation utilities for simulation results
- [utils/](mdc:utils/): Additional utility functions for the BEM package

## Visualization
- [bem/show_result.py](mdc:bem/show_result.py): Visualization tools for simulation results
  - Use `Result.view(prefix, electrode_name)` to visualize simulation results

## External Libraries
- [triangle/](mdc:triangle/): Triangulation libraries from Jonathan Shewchuk
- [fastlap/](mdc:fastlap/): FastLap BEM implementation from MIT

## Color Management
- [bem/bemColors_lib/](mdc:bem/bemColors_lib/): Contains color definitions for electrode identification
  - These colors are used to identify different electrodes in STL files
